snippet.textDisplay:
I won't give more than 7 out of 10 because of vocals. On the positive side, but not great. Harshdeep and Amit Trivedi were nice, but just not there! Jyoti Nooran (of Nooran Sisters) gave a power performance, though. Thumbs up to Bass, Drums and guitar. Awesome lyrics too. Nice song but a little disappointing on the expectations. 
Also, only 1 song an episode is very frustrating.
